8295 arm_status arm_dct4_init_q31(
8296  arm_dct4_instance_q31 * S,
8297  arm_rfft_instance_q31 * S_RFFT,
8298  arm_cfft_radix4_instance_q31 * S_CFFT,
8299  uint16_t N,
8300  uint16_t Nby2,
8301  q31_t normalize)
8302 {
8303  /* Initialise the default arm status */
8304  arm_status status = ARM_MATH_SUCCESS;
8305 
8306  /* Initializing the pointer array with the weight table base addresses of different lengths */
8307  q31_t *twiddlePtr[4] = { (q31_t *) WeightsQ31_128, (q31_t *) WeightsQ31_512,
8308  (q31_t *) WeightsQ31_2048, (q31_t *) WeightsQ31_8192
8309  };
8310 
8311  /* Initializing the pointer array with the cos factor table base addresses of different lengths */
8312  q31_t *pCosFactor[4] =
8313  { (q31_t *) cos_factorsQ31_128, (q31_t *) cos_factorsQ31_512,
8314  (q31_t *) cos_factorsQ31_2048, (q31_t *) cos_factorsQ31_8192
8315  };
8316 
8317  /* Initialize the DCT4 length */
8318  S->N = N;
8319 
8320  /* Initialize the half of DCT4 length */
8321  S->Nby2 = Nby2;
8322 
8323  /* Initialize the DCT4 Normalizing factor */
8324  S->normalize = normalize;
8325 
8326  /* Initialize Real FFT Instance */
8327  S->pRfft = S_RFFT;
8328 
8329  /* Initialize Complex FFT Instance */
8330  S->pCfft = S_CFFT;
8331 
8332  switch (N)
8333  {
8334  /* Initialize the table modifier values */
8335  case 8192u:
8336  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[3];
8337  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[3];
8338  break;
8339  case 2048u:
8340  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[2];
8341  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[2];
8342  break;
8343  case 512u:
8344  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[1];
8345  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[1];
8346  break;
8347  case 128u:
8348  S->pTwiddle = twiddlePtr[0];
8349  S->pCosFactor = pCosFactor[0];
8350  break;
8351  default:
8352  status = ARM_MATH_ARGUMENT_ERROR;
8353  }
8354 
8355  /* Initialize the RFFT/RIFFT Function */
8356  arm_rfft_init_q31(S->pRfft, S->N, 0, 1);
8357 
8358  /* return the status of DCT4 Init function */
8359  return (status);
8360 }
